Subject: Using Your Geek for Good Instead of Evil
Description: You're the leetest of leet. You dream in code. Instead of helping prolong the problems of corporations for fun and money or creating state sponsored malware, what kind of good can you do with your skills? Why bother? Come listen to some people who are changing the world by sharing their technical abilities with others.   Speakers include:Nancy Bright, Erika Carlson, Emily Gonyer, Ken Grundberg, Albert Manero, Aaron Brown, Ivan Owen - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
